{"type": "article", "id": 11366, "title": "美国同性婚姻合法，时尚圈早已“彩虹”密布", "description": "时尚品牌股价纷纷上涨", "date": "2015-06-29T13:59:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1218, "name": "同性婚姻"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}, {"id": 1686, "name": "Marc Jacobs"}], "category": 19, "author": 112576, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606154718IVBydxn54uSvOXZe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span>当地时间</span> <span>6 </span><span>月</span> <span>26 </span><span>日，美国最高法院宣布同性婚姻合法，在全美</span> <span>50 </span><span>个州同性伴侣皆可结婚。此消息发布后，珠宝品牌</span> <span>Tiffany&amp;Co </span><span>、</span> <span>Blue Nile </span><span>以及</span> <span>Signet Jewelers </span><span>的股价都上升了至少一个百分点。可以预测，未来将有更多同性伴侣结婚，这不仅对珠宝品牌，对整个时尚界而言都会带来巨大影响。</span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span>对于此次法案的决定，许多时尚设计师如</span><span> Marc Jacobs</span><span>、</span><span> Zac Posen </span><span>等都公开表示支持。时尚界历来就有更大的包容度，早有品牌使用同性恋人作为广告主题。早在</span><span>2011</span><span>年，</span><span> J.Crew </span><span>在他的设计手册中就展示了一对男性同性恋人，底下的介绍为“这是我们的设计师</span><span>Somsack </span><span>和他的男朋友，</span><span> Micah </span><span>。”</span> <span>2012 </span><span>年</span> <span>GAP </span><span>与</span><span> Banana Republic </span><span>也邀请了一对设计师的同性恋人加入广告拍摄。</span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span>而今年</span> <span>1 </span><span>月，具有高度知名度的品牌</span> <span>Tiffany&amp;Co </span><span>也加入了这一举动，在官网上推出了一对男性同性情侣相偎而坐的海报。</span> <span>Tiffany </span><span>公司表示，当下的婚姻不再是“线性的”，爱情故事也有多种形式。而推出这则广告是为了拓宽品牌的“婚姻观”。</span><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span>其实拓宽的还有市场。</span> <span>Tiffany&amp;Co 2014 </span><span>第四季度在美国市场的销售量与</span><span> 2013 </span><span>同期持平，同店销售还下降了</span><span> 1% </span><span>。而今年第一季度的财务报告显示，其总销售额与净利润都好于预期，发布的当日股价还大涨</span><span> 10.53% </span><span>。虽然这当中大大得益于其</span> <span>T </span><span>系列的热销，但也与其同性恋市场策略有关系。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span>除了广告以外，其实过去还有很多设计师的服装作品包含着彩虹的元素，宛如代表</span><span> LGBT </span><span>群体的彩虹旗，</span> <span>style.com </span><span>挑选出了 </span><span>10 </span><span>套进行了回顾。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154713L1OqmPJlrHICef4N.jpg\" title=\"Alexander McQueen Spring 2003 \" alt=\"Alexander McQueen Spring 2003 \" data-ratio=\"1.52407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Alexander McQueen Spring 2003</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154713tYdJZUBrDf2OhkeH.jpg\" title=\"Chanel Spring 2014 \" alt=\"Chanel Spring 2014 \" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Chanel Spring 2014</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154714ROH6SmM5poqQDbkj.jpg\" title=\"Burberry Prorsum Spring 2013 \" alt=\"Burberry Prorsum Spring 2013 \" data-ratio=\"0.66498316\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Burberry Prorsum Spring 2013</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154714VG8unbP2WdXYOTU6.jpg\" title=\"Jeremy Scott Fall 2012 \" alt=\"Jeremy Scott Fall 2012 \" data-ratio=\"1.49926794\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Jeremy Scott Fall 2012</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061547140KfzSlCduOwPpiMY.jpg\" title=\"Alexander McQueen Fall 2000 \" alt=\"Alexander McQueen Fall 2000 \" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:justify;\">Alexander McQueen Fall 2000</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154715j2hrKivstnxuePmc.jpg\" title=\"Pucci Spring 2014 \" alt=\"Pucci Spring 2014 \" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Pucci Spring 2014</span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154716kT0F8EagqwR7QpVH.jpg\" title=\"Prada Spring/Summer 2014 \" alt=\"Prada Spring/Summer 2014 \" data-ratio=\"1.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Prada Spring/Summer 2014</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154716lo3xaHkT0eEvsS4r.jpg\" title=\"Erdem Moralioglu Spring 2009 \" alt=\"Erdem Moralioglu Spring 2009 \" data-ratio=\"1.49926794\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Erdem Moralioglu Spring 2009</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615471712JZ9iVADFlBhCOc.jpg\" title=\"Christopher Kane Resort 2012 \" alt=\"Christopher Kane Resort 2012 \" data-ratio=\"1.49926794\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Christopher Kane Resort 2012 </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606154717IK0DH1ugQNhV8oqS.jpg\" title=\"Meadham Kirchhoff Fall 2012 \" alt=\"Meadham Kirchhoff Fall 2012 \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.49926794\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span style=\"text-align:center;\">Meadham Kirchhoff Fall 2012 </span><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">据统计，全球范围内</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">LGBT </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">人口已超过</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">4 </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">亿，拥有</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">3 </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">万亿美元的消费能力。不少同性恋者往往还拥有更多的可支配收入，讲究穿着与潮流。对于时尚界而言，这无疑是一个不可低估且亟待开发的消费市场。在刚过去的</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">2016 </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">春夏米兰男装周上，</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> Prada</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">、</span><span style=\"text-align:start;\"> Gucci </span><span style=\"text-align:start;\">等多个大牌已用轻柔的男装刮起了“无性别”风格，也许这正是未来“彩虹经济”的一场预告。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}